OL,6,FA paedophile who abused a teenage girl
OL,7,Fmore than 20 years ago has been
OL,8,Fjailed.JRobert Jones, 44, was
OL,9,Fconvicted of indecent assault and
OL,10,Fgross indecency with a child following
OL,11,Fa trial at Newcastle Crown Court.
OL,13,FIt is after Jones subjected a teenage
OL,14,Fgirl to two instances of sexual abuse
OL,15,Fin between 1998 and 1999 when he was
OL,16,Fin his late teens.
OL,18,FAfter almost two decades, the victim
OL,19,Freported the crimes in 2021 and an
OL,20,Finvestigation was launched.
