OL,3,CPaedophile who abused teenager more
OL,4,Cthan 20 years ago jailed
OL,6,FJones was arrested the same night but
OL,7,Fdenied the allegations put towards him.
OL,9,FIn 2022, Jones was charged with two
OL,10,Foffences consisting of gross indecency
OL,11,Fwith a child and indecent assault on a
OL,12,Fchild as the offences took place
OL,13,Fbefore the Sexual Offences Act was
OL,14,Fintroduced in 2003.JHe continued to
OL,15,Fdeny the allegations.
OL,17,FFollowing a trial at Newcastle Crown
OL,18,FCourt earlier this year, he was
OL,19,Fconvicted of both offences.
