OL,3,CPaedophile who abused teenager more
OL,4,Cthan 20 years ago jailed
OL,6,FOn Tuesday 7 May, Jones, of Berechurch
OL,7,FRoad, Colchester, Essex, was sentenced
OL,8,Fto three and a half years behind bars,
OL,9,Fmade to sign the Sex Offender's
OL,10,FRegister for life and given a Sexual
OL,11,FHarm Prevention Order (SHPO) and
OL,12,Frestraining order.
OL,14,Fpraised the bravery of his victim, and
OL,15,Fsaid 'no matter how much time has
OL,16,Fpassed, we're here for you.'
